text: Albino da Silva (born 9 January 1925) is a Portuguese former sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre rifle, prone event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Portuguese male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Portugal Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Porto
